的本质是继承?\" 仓促打字，如果各位捧场，题目会改的更有逻辑一些"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-34cd7169e2c16aee7b7b085f8bf41378_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/316680205"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItLqb5KqIipkoEAMaCDMyNjQ5NzYwIKq7xuQFMAA45AhAGnIJMzE2NjgwMjA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1733195262.287790", "card_id": "Q_5651489977", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 121}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大家更喜欢纸质书还是电子书?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "电子书方便纸质书有质感，两者都不错"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-2a708983a265dbb250e7504a106a1efb_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.5 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5651489977"}}, "attached_info": "CkEItLqb5KqIipkoEAMaCTExMjEwNjg0MSD+zbC6BjAAOKMBQBtyCjU2NTE0ODk5Nzd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1733195262.288152", "card_id": "Q_384673958", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 77}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "请问您见过最惊艳的 SQL 查询语句是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a28fba2f26facb181ba0ad8b907a3f6a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/384673958"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8ItLqb5KqIipkoEAMaCDQ3NzYxMDI1ILLtl/QFMAA4nwxAHHIJMzg0NjczOTU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1733195262.288381", "card_id": "Q_5708110363", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 164}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "青岛发布首批「妈妈岗」用人目录，上班灵活、工作弹性，多地已开展探索，此制度有何影响？如何推广完善？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，山东省青岛市人力资源和社会保障局发布青岛市首批「妈妈岗」用人目录（一），请广大求职者予以关注。 「妈妈岗」并非新词，此前，广东、河北、黑龙江等地均进行了相关探索。此次青岛发布用人目录，意味着「妈妈岗」用人工作又迎新推进。 190 个岗位来自 7 个用人单位 据报道，青岛市积极推行「妈妈岗」创新做法，广泛征集、发布上班灵活、工作弹性、有质量有温度的适合「宝妈」等群体的就业岗位。 梳理该目录发现，此轮目录共发布了 190 个岗位需求，来自 7 个用人单位，涉及餐饮、家政、保安服务等领域，多为钟点工和小时工。 其他地区也在征集相关岗位 11 月 20 日，山东临沂沂河新区也发布公告，面向社会征集「妈妈岗」。 根据公告内容，这些岗位要求工作时间灵活，适合「宝妈」居家就业的项目，如居家客服、电商直播、手工制品制作、自媒体创作等兼顾家庭与工作的岗位。 同时，征集工作时间可弹性安排、劳动强度适中、工作环境良好的，可以适当安排双休、接娃送娃等便于育儿、持家的专业技术、管理、销售、生产类等岗位。 灵活上班、弹性工作！「妈妈岗」来了！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-395831bc187a990ca73eebe0a48038f2_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "3.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/5708110363"}}, "attached_info": "CkEItLqb5KqIipkoEAMaCTExMjExODIyMyC8p7S6BjAAOP8CQB1yCjU3MDgxMTAzNjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1724871100431802368", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHITMTcyNDg3MTEwMDQzMTgwMjM2OHgA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}]}